examples.en: His chronic tardiness has put him in poor standing with his boss, who values hustle and promptitude.
I'd be willing to pass over this latest episode of tardiness if there hadn't been so many before.
His tardiness was just another in a series of small discourtesies.
Her perpetual tardiness maddened her friends to no end.
I castigated him for his constant tardiness.
He reprimanded the summer intern for her constant tardiness.
